Enable or disable association group command and central scene command<br /> <h1>Overview</h1><p>0 - Group Association Only<br />1- Central Scene Only<br />2 - Group Association and Central Scene</p><p><br /></p>
        ]]></description>
        <default>2</default>
        <options>
