Select indicator color for the Bottom Button<br /> <h1>Overview</h1><p>0- Disabled<br />1- Red<br /> 2- Blue<br /> 3- Green<br /> 4- Pink<br /> 5- Cyan<br /> 6- Purple<br /> 7- Orange<br /> 8- Yellow<br /> 9- White</p>
